'''Psi''' was a letter in the [[Tionese/Legends|Tionese alphabet]]. Psi was often used as a [[Callsign/Legends|call sign]] for [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Flight group/Legends|Flight groups]], specifically [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboats]]. Assault Gunboat designated ''Psi 2'' is one such example.

